    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        My name is <b>Ooucholive, </b> I am an apparel designer with nearly two years of experience, including the past year working with an international brand. Specializing in sportswear, I create elegant, minimalist designs that combine functionality and style. With a focus on detail and innovation, I aim to deliver designs that reflect identity and inspire performance.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.instagram.com/livgraph/" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
